      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, currently maintained in impeccable showroom condition. This unit has been curated for the most discerning enthusiast, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory luster. Meticulously serviced and preserved with uncompromising attention to detail, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of unparalleled quality. Inspections will confirm its status as a premier example of the marque.",
